high_descs: turn around go to the counter top to the left of the stove
pick up the coffee mug from the counter top
turn back around and take the mug to the fridge
put the mug in the fridge; wait for it to chill; remove the mug
turn around and take the mug to the table top with the coffee maker on it
place the mug in the coffee maker so it can catch coffee
anns.task_desc: place a chilled mug on the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the small section of counter to the left of the oven.
Pick up the mug off of the counter in front of you.
Turn around and walk over to the black fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge and let it get cold for a couple seconds, then open the fridge and take out the cold mug, then close the fridge doors.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn left to face the white table.
Put the cold mug into the coffee machine that is on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold mug into a coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn around then go across the room to the counter left of he stove.
Pick up the coffee mug that is beside the bowl on the counter.
Go across the room to the refrigerator.
Open the fridge then place the coffee mug on the fourth shelf, close the fridge then wait, now open the fridge and pick up the coffee mug. Close the fridge
Go across the room to the table with the coffee machine.
Place the mug in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled coffee mug in the coffee machine.
